.SS Key Principles
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Use const for references that won't be reassigned
.IP \(bu 2
Use let for references that will be reassigned
.IP \(bu 2
Prefer arrow functions over function expressions
.IP \(bu 2
Use template literals instead of string concatenation
.IP \(bu 2
Use destructuring for objects and arrays
.IP \(bu 2
Use default parameters instead of mutating arguments
.IP \(bu 2
Use spread operator for array and object copying
.IP \(bu 2
Single quotes for strings
.IP \(bu 2
No semicolons at end of statements (handled by Prettier)
.RE
.SS React Guidelines
.RS
.IP \(bu 2
Use JSX for React components
.IP \(bu 2
Use PascalCase for component names
.IP \(bu 2
Use camelCase for prop names
.IP \(bu 2
